projectGridLines.title: Founder's Office
projectGridLines.description:
Description: You will be working directly with the Founding Team on multitude of projects

ranging from writing PRDs, researching on product offerings, strategic partnerships,

building relationships and immediate requirements as and when they come. It is an ideal

position for Generalists and students looking to enter the Founder's Office and Consulting

field. It will be a lot of end to end management with main focus on execution.

Skill sets: Business Development, Research, Product Management, Communication

(Oral & Written)

projectGridLines.title: Marketing
projectGridLines.description:
Skill sets: Must have: SEO, Social Media Analytics & Tools, SMM Strategy, Good to

have: Google & Meta Ads, Graphic Designing
